535
00:42:52,450 --> 00:42:55,875
and forget about the person who has always been by our side.

536
00:42:56,908 --> 00:42:58,665
Xu Man?

537
00:43:01,908 --> 00:43:05,500
Don't worry. You can tell me anything.

538
00:43:08,751 --> 00:43:12,208
