00:43:44,366 --> 00:43:46,292
When it comes to confessing,

550
00:43:47,700 --> 00:43:49,458
I have a trauma.

551
00:43:53,825 --> 00:43:56,158
All right.

552
00:43:56,158 --> 00:43:58,250
So, does Hai Nuo

553
00:43:59,658 --> 00:44:02,958
